item.description: The Biteship: Plugin Ongkos Kirim Kurir Instant, Reguler, Kargo WordPress plugin before 2.2.25 does not sanitise and escape the biteship_error and biteship_message parameters before outputting them back in the page, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin
